<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>01&gt;税费</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>02&gt;贷款：公积金贷款、商业贷款</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>03&gt;保刚需公证摇号：刚需、非刚需</strong></p>
